custom_steps:
Get all players in ebis who require consent:
GET request to ebis2-core-services/dpl/consentrequired/{year}
Returns a list:
                [
                                {
                                                orgId: 1,
                                                playerId, 12345,
                                                consentYear, 2020
                                },
                                {
                                                orgId: 2,
                                                playerId, 12346,
                                                consentYear, 2020
                                },
                                ..
                                etc
                ]
Update a players consent (use the same object as the list returned above):
                POST request to ebis2-core-services/dpl/player/consent
                Payload is a single consent object:
                                {
                                                orgId: 1,
                                                playerId, 12345,
                                                consentYear, 2019
                                }
